\c 3  
\p
\v 2-3 Kurijin nyampali nyarra wantuliny yija yiji kurlumajirri. Paliny yija yirti kaniny marrngu wantuliny, paliny nyampali waljaku palinykungarra...munu yawurrkata,...munu kulikata...   